msgstr "Mata a todos los enemigos."

#. Description for command variant "mvz2:kill contraption"
#: Commands meta file
msgctxt "command_variant.description"
msgid "杀死所有器械。"
msgstr "Mata todos los artilugios."

#. Description for command variant "mvz2:kill obstacle"
#: Commands meta file
